in your measurement.

84
00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:54.000
Any measurement that you make

85
00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:56.000
without any knowledge
of the uncertainty

86
00:04:53.000 --> 00:04:59.000
is meaningless.

